2. Environment Setup
ğŸ”¹ Mac Setup (for Android & iOS)

Install Homebrew

/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"


Install Node.js & npm (needed for Appium)

brew install node


Install Appium (CLI)

npm install -g appium


Install Appium Doctor (checks setup)

npm install -g appium-doctor
appium-doctor --android
appium-doctor --ios


Install Android Studio â†’ setup SDK, AVD (emulator).

For iOS: Install Xcode + Xcode command line tools.

Python setup

brew install python3
pip install Appium-Python-Client pytest python-dotenv

ğŸ”¹ Windows Setup (for Android only)

Install Node.js â†’ nodejs.org
.

Install Appium & Doctor

npm install -g appium
npm install -g appium-doctor


Install Java JDK 11+ â†’ set JAVA_HOME.

Install Android Studio â†’ setup SDK path & environment variables:

ANDROID_HOME = C:\Users\YourName\AppData\Local\Android\Sdk

Add platform-tools & tools/bin to PATH.

Install Python (3.9+ recommended).

pip install Appium-Python-Client pytest python-dotenv
